{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"CAnnotated Narrative Steps\n    \n      How it works\n      \n        \n          \n          Step 01\n          Capture field signals\n          Proprietary network of researchers, automated data streams, and structured surveys generate raw intelligence from the ground up.\n        \n        \n          \n          Step 02\n          Synthesize with AI\n          FuzzyOwl's semantic engine and FWBM models process, classify, and structure intelligence across dimensions.\n        \n        \n          \n          Step 03\n          Deliver decision support\n          OWL Agent translates structured intelligence into actionable answers for strategy, investment, and research.\n        \n      \n    \n    \n      Annotated Narrative Steps\n      Numbered vertical timeline with editorial prose annotations. Reveals step by step on scroll. More human, more readable, less \"tech diagram.\" Good for communicating process to non-technical audiences. Lower implementation complexity — strong Framer Motion entrance animations carry the weight.\n      \n        Human & readableScroll-revealedLow complexityEditorial","choice":"c","id":null,"timestamp":1774269432317}
